It’s been five years since everything was awesome and the citizens are now facing a huge new threat: LEGO DUPLO invaders from outer space, wrecking everything faster than it can be rebuilt. The battle to defeat the invaders and restore harmony to the LEGO universe will take Emmet, Lucy, Batman and their friends to faraway, unexplored worlds, including a strange galaxy where everything is musical. It will test their courage, creativity and Master Building skills, and reveal just how special they really are.  To enter the Competition, and stand a chance of winning the prize, eligible entrants will be required to: Book to watch the movie, Lego Movie 2 releasing on the 01st March at any of our Ster-Kinekor Theatres cinemas, and submit your reference ticket number via WhatsApp to 081 728 2888. There is no limit to the number of times entrants may enter the Competition during the Competition Period, however, the number of entries will not increase an entrant’s chances of winning any of the prizes as mentioned below in the Competition Rules.  Starring: Chris Pratt, Elizabeth Banks, Will Arnett, Nick Offerman, Alison Brie, Tiffany Haddish and Stephanie Beatriz
Directed by: Mike Mitchell     